---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Manual testing — MCP Studio" current="manual-testing">

  <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--muted-foreground)] mb-4">
    [ Manual testing ]
  </p>
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-4">Manual testing</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)] max-w-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
    [Intro: test tools, resources, and widget responses without writing any test code.]
  </p>

  <!-- Tools -->
  <section id="tools" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-1">Tool calls</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-lg">
      [How to pick a tool from the sidebar, fill in arguments, and run it. Mention the Args / Definition tabs.]
    </p>
    <!-- placeholder screenshot / diagram -->
    <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--border)] h-40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
      screenshot: tool call editor
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources -->
  <section id="resources" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-1">Resources</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-lg">
      [How to pick a resource, enter a URI, and read its contents. Mention the result pane.]
    </p>
    <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--border)] h-40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
      screenshot: resource reader
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Widget resource -->
  <section id="widget" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-1">Widget resource</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-lg">
      [Explain widget resources: inject mock tool data, pick platform (Claude/OpenAI), theme, viewport, and interact live in the preview pane.]
    </p>

    <div class="border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)] p-4 mb-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--muted-foreground)] mb-3">Test data tab</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed max-w-md">
        [Describe the Test Data editor: inject <code class="text-[var(--foreground)] bg-[var(--secondary)] px-1">toolInput</code>, <code class="text-[var(--foreground)] bg-[var(--secondary)] px-1">toolOutput</code>, and <code class="text-[var(--foreground)] bg-[var(--secondary)] px-1">widgetState</code> as JSON to simulate different AI responses without calling a real model.]
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)] p-4 mb-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--muted-foreground)] mb-3">Platform and viewport</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed max-w-md">
        [Describe platform selector (Claude / OpenAI) and viewport presets (Mobile / Tablet / Desktop / Custom). Mention compatibility badges.]
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--border)] h-40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
      screenshot: widget preview pane
    </div>
  </section>

</DocsLayout>
